Cactbot timeline files vendored from https://github.com/OverlayPlugin/cactbot
(directory ui/raidboss/data/...), licensed under the Apache 2.0 License
with a partial-source clause.

These files are the authoritative encounter timelines maintained by the cactbot
community. Used by Vigil to annotate fight_model rows with human-readable
mechanic names + expected phase-relative timings. We redistribute them as-is.

Upstream license: https://github.com/OverlayPlugin/cactbot/blob/main/LICENSE

Files:
  r9s.txt                       — M9S Vamp Fatale
  r10s.txt                      — M10S Red Hot and Deep Blue
  r11s.txt                      — M11S The Tyrant
  r12s.txt                      — M12S Lindwurm + M12S-P2 (Lindwurm II)
  futures_rewritten.txt         — FRU
  the_omega_protocol.txt        — TOP
  dragonsongs_reprise_ultimate.txt — DSR

To refresh: run `.\scripts\refresh_cactbot.ps1` from the project root
(it re-fetches every file from upstream raw.githubusercontent.com and
reports per-file size diffs). Use `-DryRun` to preview, `-Only <name>`
to refresh a single file.
